Single Player Chess in C++.

GUI made with SFML.

Piece sprite image source and license can be found at https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Chess_Pieces_Sprite.svg

Features needing implementation:
-Check for niche stalemate scenarios involving more than a King left
-Pawn promotion
-Checking if a castle will put the player in check
-GUI features (Pawn promotion, Surrender, Game end screen)
-Home screen
-Option to play against chess engine